trans-unit.source: Provides a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D"></xref> that renders <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D"></xref>呈現<xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"></xref>物件。

trans-unit.source: Provides services and properties that are common to all visual objects, including hit-testing, coordinate transformation, and bounding-box calculations.
trans-unit.target: 提供服務和屬性通用於所有的 visual 物件，包括點擊測試協調轉換 」 和 「 週框方塊的計算。

trans-unit.source: The ModelVisual3D class has a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D.Children%2A> property that enables you to build a tree structure of ModelVisual3D objects.
trans-unit.target: ModelVisual3D 類別具有<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D.Children%2A>可讓您建置 ModelVisual3D 物件的樹狀結構的屬性。</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D.Children%2A>

trans-unit.source: ModelVisual3D objects are optimized as scene nodes.
trans-unit.target: ModelVisual3D 物件已最佳化為場景節點。

trans-unit.source: For example, they cache bounds.
trans-unit.target: 例如，便會快取範圍。

trans-unit.source: Whenever you can, use ModelVisual3D objects for unique instances of objects within your scene.
trans-unit.target: 請盡可能使用 ModelVisual3D 物件的唯一執行個體的場景中的物件。

trans-unit.source: This usage contrasts with that of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D> objects, which are lightweight objects that are optimized to be shared and reused.
trans-unit.target: 這種使用方式的相反<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D>物件，其中是輕量型共用及重複使用而最佳化的物件。</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D>

trans-unit.source: For example, use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D> object to build a model of a car; and use ten ModelVisual3D objects to place ten cars in your scene.
trans-unit.target: 例如，使用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D>物件來建立汽車; 的模型，並使用十 ModelVisual3D 物件放置在場景中的十個汽車。</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D>
